==English==
=== Noun ===
'''oat''' (Plural: [[oats]])

# A widely cultivated cereal grass, ''[[Avena sativa]]''.
# The seeds of the oat, harvested as a food crop. Used also in form [[oats]].

====Scientific names====
*[[Avena sativa]]

====Related terms====
*[[oatmeal]]
*[[be off one's oats]]
*[[feel one's oats]]
*[[sow one's wild oats]]

